OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778652345
OL,3,CWoman wanted for more than 20 years
OL,4,Carrested in live facial recognition
OL,5,Cpilot
OL,7,FA woman wanted for more than 20 years
OL,8,Fhas been arrested during a six-month
OL,9,Ftrial of live facial recognition in
OL,10,Fsouth London.
OL,12,FIn total 173 suspects were arrested
OL,13,Ffor crimes including kidnap, rape and
OL,14,Fserious sexual assault during the
OL,15,Fpilot in Croydon, during which static
OL,16,Fcameras rather than vans were used for
OL,17,Fthe first time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
