OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778652345
OL,3,CWoman wanted for more than 20 years
OL,4,Carrested in live facial recognition
OL,5,Cpilot
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police said that
OL,8,Fcrime in the area reduced by 10.5%
OL,9,Fduring the trial, which took place
OL,10,Fbetween October 2025 and March 2026,
OL,11,Fincluding a 21% reduction in violence
OL,12,Fagainst women and girls.
OL,14,FThe static cameras, placed on Croydon
OL,15,FHigh Street, were used in 24
OL,16,Foperations, with arrests including a
OL,17,F36-year-old woman who was wanted for
OL,18,Ffailing to appear at court for an
OL,19,Fassault in 2004.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
