CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778652345
OL,3,CWoman wanted for more than 20 years
OL,4,Carrested in live facial recognition
OL,5,Cpilot
OL,7,FA 31-year-old man who was wanted for
OL,8,Fvoyeurism for more than six months was
OL,9,Falso arrested, as well as a 41-year-
OL,10,Fold man who was wanted in connection
OL,11,Fwith a rape in November in Croydon.
OL,13,FLindsey Chiswick, national and Met
OL,14,Flead for live facial recognition,
OL,15,Fsaid: "These results show why live
OL,16,Ffacial recognition is such a powerful
OL,17,Ftool when it's used carefully, openly
OL,18,Fand in the right places.
OL,26,@wD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
