OL,3,CWoman wanted for more than 20 years
OL,4,Carrested in live facial recognition
OL,5,Cpilot
OL,7,F"Crime in this area is down by more
OL,8,Fthan 10%, and the public can see the
OL,9,Fdifference.
OL,11,F"This technology is helping us find
OL,12,Fpeople wanted by the courts, identify
OL,13,Fserious offenders quickly and focus
OL,14,Four resources where they make the
OL,15,Fbiggest impact, all with exceptional
OL,16,Faccuracy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
