OL,3,CWoman wanted for more than 20 years
OL,4,Carrested in live facial recognition
OL,5,Cpilot
OL,7,F"We will continue using static cameras
OL,8,Fin Croydon as part of our regular live
OL,9,Ffacial recognition deployments which
OL,10,Fplay a vital part in keeping London
OL,11,Fsafe."
OL,13,FMore than 470,000 people walked past
OL,14,Fthe camera during the pilot, which saw
OL,15,Fone false alert for which the person
OL,16,Fwas spoken to by officers and then
OL,17,Fallowed to leave.
